John Orcsik https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Orcsik 0 John Orcsik (born 3 May 1945) is an Hungarian Australian actor, writer and director best known for his television roles but also prominently for the film version of the soap opera Number 96. He was married to actress Paula Duncan.
